quran[21]{c,v,t}:
  52,29,"Anndintin tun, sabu neema Joomi maa on, a wonaa ndureejo wanaa a feetu…óo"
  52,30,"Kaa …ďe wi'ay wonnde : \"Ko yimoowo ! Men habbitani mo tun jikke maayde"
  52,31,"Maaku : \"Awa habbitee ! Min kadi mi…óo habbitodi e mon"
  52,32,Kaa ko haqqille ma…ď…ďe …óen yamir…ďe …óum? Kaa hara ko …ďe yim…ďe bewu…ďe tun
  52,33,"Kaa …ďe wi'ay wonnde : \"O sincu nde?\" Si ko woni, wanaa …ďe gom…óinoo…ďe"
  52,34,"Awa yo …ďe addii yewtere sugu mayre, si wonii ko …ďe goongu…ďe"
  52,35,Kaa …ďe tagira …ďaawo tagu…óo? Kaa ko kam…ďe woni tagu…ďe …ďen
  52,36,"Kaa (ko) kam…ďe tagi kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin? Ko woni kon, …ďe yananaaka"
  52,37,Kaa …ďe jogiti ngaluuji Joomi maa …óin? Kaa ko kam…ďe woni hu…ďindii…ďe …ďen
  52,38,Kaa …ďe jogiti …ďargal ngal …ďe jentorta? Awa yo he…óitii…óo ma…ď…ďe on addu hujja …ďanngu…óo
  52,39,"Kaa hara ko …ďi…ó…ďe rew…ďe woodanta Mo, onon kan wor…ďe …ďen"
  52,40,"Kaa a lamndi …ďe njo…ďdi, hara yo…ďugol ndi no teddani …ďe"
  52,41,"Kaa …ďe anndu fii wirnii…ói …óin, hara hi…ďe winnda"
  52,42,"Kaa …ďe faala fewjoore? Doo ko yeddu…ďe …ďen, woni fooletee…ďe pewje …ďen"
  52,43,"Kaa hi…ďe mari rewetee…óo ko woori Allah? Senaade woodanii Allah, e kon ko …ďe sirkata"
  52,44,"Si …ďe yi'ii ta∆īatine immornde ka kammu no yani, …ďe wi'a: \"Ko duule fawondir…óe"
  52,45,"Terto …ďe, haa …ďe hawroya e √Īalaande ma…ď…ďe nde …ďe leptoytee e mun"
  52,46,"√Ďalnde nde pewje ma…ď…ďe duncanoytaa …ďe hay huunde, …ďe wonaa kadi walloytee…ďe"
  52,47,"Ko pellet, hino woodani too√Īu…ďe …ďen, lepte goo ko wanaa …óen …óon. Kono ko …ďuri …óuu…óude kon e ma…ď…ďe, …ďe anndaa"
  52,48,"Mu√Ī√Īo √Īaawoore Joomi maa nden. Tawde pellet, hi…óa e ndenka Amen. Seniniraa yettugol Joomi maa, tuma …ďaŇčoto…óaa"
  52,49,"Jemma on kadi, subbunhinano…óaa Mo e ka mutugol koode"